snippet.title: Vagrant Moon Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2879750/Vagrant_Moon/

Vagrant Moon is a charming 3D platformer that captures the classic feel and simplicity of PS1-era games. The game invites you on a serene treasure hunt through its vibrant landscapes, where every treasure not only enhances your abilities but also unlocks new areas of the enchanted valley to explore.

Available on Steam May 8th 2024
